{"tid":417066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［落閘放狗］西班牙封票站關網頁禁公投「一票都不能有」","createTime":"2017-09-28T10:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T10:42:18.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ada5a44488f92eb4adbc668cc3ead26593abff1f","tid":417066,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治區下月1日舉行獨立公投，馬德里中央政府繼續封殺這場「違憲」公投，不但關閉票站以及網站，加泰羅尼亞檢察長更下令向提供地方當票站的學校提出刑事檢控。<br />\n<br />\n馬德里當局認定公投違法，檢方將焦點集中在票站上，下令警方在公投前一天封鎖票站大樓，並在選舉當天部署警員阻止民眾投票。<br />\n此外，檢方也揚言對提供投票地點的加泰羅尼亞多位市長、學校與大學主任提出刑事檢控。由加泰羅尼亞分離主義者監督投票成立的選舉委員會，在西班牙憲法法庭威脅每天罰款1.2萬歐元（11萬港元）後已解散。<br />\n警方亦加緊執行封殺公投的指示，目前已沒收近1,000萬張選票，也關閉59個提供公投相關資訊的網站，另有85個網站正在關閉階段。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/181629_7c57b0e3a0872e99686fd70a62a88638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F181629_7c57b0e3a0872e99686fd70a62a88638.jpg&h=7aade297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170927/57261456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170927%2F57261456&d=g497ee0v2v%2FLjIX%2FxLisjYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=af057be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170927%2F57261456&h=1a183106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170927/57261456</a><br />\n西班牙終於恢復高壓統治"},{"pid":"b6721af8905cd1f12e9c13e53b0f44756599f707","tid":417066,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:22:41.000Z","msg":"加泰快攪革命吧"},{"pid":"8cf44ade29125ff5c0a1bdac453065502fe59b14","tid":417066,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3feedbbad734b7088e92c2da52a8104a4b4e8